PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our iPhone Cases
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What materials are your iPhone cases made from?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our iPhone cases are crafted from high-quality materials including durable polycarbonate, flexible TPU, and premium genuine leather. We select materials that offer the perfect balance of protection and style.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Do your cases support wireless charging?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, all of our iPhone cases are designed to be fully compatible with wireless charging. You can charge your iPhone without removing the case, ensuring convenience and protection at all times.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How do I know which case will fit my iPhone model?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: We offer cases for all current iPhone models. Simply select your iPhone model from the dropdown menu on each product page to ensure a perfect fit. If you're unsure about your model, check your iPhone settings or contact our customer support for assistance.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What is your return policy for iPhone cases?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We offer a 30-day return policy on all our iPhone cases. If you're not completely satisfied with your purchase, you can return the case in its original condition for a full refund or exchange. Please refer to our Returns page for detailed instructions.
